    <answer>
      <p>
        <m>\frac{1}{2}\left(\frac{x^2}{2} - \frac{1}{x}\right) + \frac{1}{4}</m>. <m>\Pr\left(1 \leq X \leq \frac{3}{2}\right) \approx 0.479.</m>
